{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, LLMs can be used for factchecking to counteract the spreading of misinformation, i.e.",
    "to check the validity of claims made through various media and social media platforms (Chavalarias 2022; Leippold et al. 2024; Schimanski et al. 2024).",
    "In this section, we demonstrate the performance and limitations of using chatbots through practical experiments, utilising the IPCC reports as a testbed for these technologies.",
    "These experiments can of course also be adapted accordingly to other GEAs.",
    "In a first experiment, three different instructions are provided to ChatClimate on how to answer a query."
  ]
}